bUHLsGA4 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Flarge-banner.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Flarge-banner.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4"/></div><div class="work-case-body"><aside class="work-case-sidebar" aria-label="Project details"><p class="work-case-eyebrow">Vigil</p><dl class="work-case-meta"><div class="work-case-meta-row"><dt>Timeline</dt><dd>Concept</dd></div><div class="work-case-meta-row"><dt id="work-case-categories-vigil">Categories</dt><dd><ul class="work-case-category-list" aria-labelledby="work-case-categories-vigil"><li>Concept</li><li>Product Design</li><li>Web Design</li><li>Dev Tools</li><li>AI</li></ul></dd></div><div class="work-case-meta-row"><dt>Location</dt><dd>Concept · Spec Work</dd></div><div class="work-case-meta-row"><dt>Year</dt><dd>2026</dd></div></dl></aside><div class="work-case-main"><div class="work-case-intro"><h1 class="work-case-title" id="work-case-title"><span class="TextReveal-module-scss-module__WSa0mG__line" data-text-reveal-line="true"><span class="TextReveal-module-scss-module__WSa0mG__inner" data-text-reveal-inner="true" style="filter:blur(14px);opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px)">Stop finding out</span></span><span class="TextReveal-module-scss-module__WSa0mG__line" data-text-reveal-line="true"><span class="TextReveal-module-scss-module__WSa0mG__inner" data-text-reveal-inner="true" style="filter:blur(14px);opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px)">from your users</span></span></h1><p class="work-case-lede">Vigil is a concept for an AI-native observability platform — designed to explore what error monitoring looks like when the tool explains the problem, not just reports it. We took the product from name through to a complete web presence and dashboard design: a system that reads your logs, traces, and errors in real time and tells you what broke, why, and how to fix it before your users notice.</p></div><div class="work-case-sections"><section class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__section" aria-labelledby="_R_qislubsnlnb_" aria-describedby="_R_qislubsnlnbH1_"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__inner"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__intro"><h2 id="_R_qislubsnlnb_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__title">Brief</h2><p id="_R_qislubsnlnbH1_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__subtitle">Observability that thinks, not just watches</p><p class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__paragraph">Most monitoring tools give you noise when you need signal. They tell you something broke — not why, and not what to do. Vigil was designed to close that gap: an AI layer that reads the full context of an incident and surfaces a clear root cause analysis, not a wall of stack traces to debug at 2am. We defined the product positioning, wrote the web copy, and designed the dashboard and incident detail screens from the ground up.</p></div></div></section><section class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__section" aria-labelledby="_R_1aislubsnlnb_" aria-describedby="_R_1aislubsnlnbH1_"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__inner"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__intro"><h2 id="_R_1aislubsnlnb_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__title">Positioning</h2><p id="_R_1aislubsnlnbH1_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__subtitle">&quot;Stop finding out from your users&quot;</p><p class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__paragraph">The headline captures the specific shame every engineering team has felt: a customer finds the bug before the monitoring does. We wrote it to land immediately and position Vigil as the tool that closes that gap. The web design matches the product&#x27;s character — dark, technical, and alert-driven, with a live incident visible on first scroll so the value proposition is shown, not explained.</p></div><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figureWrap"><figure class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figure"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__imageFrame"><img alt="Vigil — hero section with headline and active incident" loading="lazy" width="1600" height="900" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__image" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=384&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fhero.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4"/></div></figure></div></div></section><section class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__section" aria-labelledby="_R_1qislubsnlnb_" aria-describedby="_R_1qislubsnlnbH1_"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__inner"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__intro"><h2 id="_R_1qislubsnlnb_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__title">Incident overview</h2><p id="_R_1qislubsnlnbH1_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__subtitle">Error rate, active incidents, service health</p><p class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__paragraph">The main dashboard is designed for triage speed. A time-series graph shows error rate across the last 24 hours — flat line interrupted by a spike is the story every on-call engineer dreads. Active incidents list below, each with an AI-generated severity score and a one-line summary of the likely cause. Service health cards at the bottom give a system-wide read at a glance. Nothing is buried; everything surfaces the moment it matters.</p></div><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figureWrap"><figure class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figure"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__imageFrame"><img alt="Vigil — incident dashboard with error rate graph and active incidents" loading="lazy" width="1600" height="900" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__image" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=384&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4 3840w" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fcase-studies%2Fvigil%2Fdashboard-overview.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75&amp;dpl=dpl_A6aUt6FdMbVkQ1PPeFnRbUHLsGA4"/></div></figure></div></div></section><section class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__section" aria-labelledby="_R_2aislubsnlnb_" aria-describedby="_R_2aislubsnlnbH1_"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__inner"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__intro"><h2 id="_R_2aislubsnlnb_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__title">AI root cause analysis</h2><p id="_R_2aislubsnlnbH1_" class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__subtitle">What happened, why, and how to fix it</p><p class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__paragraph">The incident detail screen is where Vigil earns its value. Instead of a raw log dump, the AI surfaces a structured three-part analysis: what happened, why it happened, and what to do about it — specific, not generic. The error trace sits below for engineers who want the full context. We designed this screen to be useful in the worst moment: the one where production is down and the on-call engineer needs an answer in seconds, not after reading 400 log lines.</p></div><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figureWrap"><figure class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__figure"><div class="CaseStudySection-module-scss-module__KrPwpG__imageFrame"><img alt="Vigil — AI root cause analysis for active incident" loading="lazy" width="16